resource.chars: This section contains praises of pie memorie Dompnus Gaufredus Abbas de Rufford, Sunt et alii tales hodie in anglia duo uel tres cisterciensis ordinis [margin: pluresque forsitan aliorum ordinum et secularium] quorum nomina quia adhuc supersunt reticeo; of St Edmund of Canterbury, Roger Niger, bishop of London, and Robertus grossum capud of Lincoln
